item.title: [+898] Interracial Couple Denied Marriage License
item.description: HAMMOND, La. A Louisiana justice of the peace said he refused to issue a marriage license to an interracial couple out of concern for any children the couple might have. Note, I love the assumption that they can't have children without getting married, and must have children if the do get married.

item.title: [+698] Why The Office Isn't The Show It Used To Be
item.description: When it started, The Office was a show about regular people like you and me working in a dead-end job at a generic company. Now, it looks like Jim and Pam are the only normal ones in the bunch. Every other character on the show has turned into an over-the-top caricature of those personality quirks that used to make them relatable.

item.title: [+588] 45 Foods You Can Make Yourself (But Never Thought You Could)
